#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; is, well, a jukebox. As is typical with many jukebox applications, "
"&juk; allows you to edit the <quote>tags</quote> of your audio files, and "
"manage your collection and playlists."
msgstr ""
"&juk; je dzuboks. Kao što je tipično sa mnogim džuboks aplikacijama, &juk; "
"vam dopušta da uređujete <quote>tags</quote> vaših audio datoteka, i "
"upravljate vašim kolekcijama i listama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &juk;"
msgstr "Korištenje &juk;"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &juk;"
msgstr "Ovdje je slika ekrana &juk;-a"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of &juk; in action."
msgstr "Slika ekrana &juk;-a u akciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; maintains a list of all files that it knows about. This is called the "
"<guilabel>Collection List</guilabel>. The collection list is specific to "
"&juk; and is not shared with other applications."
msgstr ""
"&juk; odrđava listu svih datoteka koje poznaje. Ovo se zove "
"<guilabel>Collection List</guilabel>. Lista kolekcija je specifična za &juk; "
"i ne dijeli se sa ostalim aplikacijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Independent of the Collection List, are playlists. You can have as many "
"playlists as you want. You can use &juk; created playlists with other media "
"players (such as &amarok; or <application>xmms</application>) and you can "
"manage playlists created in those applications from within &juk;."
msgstr ""
"Nezavisne od listi kolekcija, su muzičke liste. Možete imati onoliko listi "
"koliko želite. Možete koristiti &juk; kreirane liste sa drugim medijskim "
"playerima ( kao što su &amarok; ili <application>xmms</application>) i "
"možete upravljati listama kreiranim u tim aplikacijama iz &juk;-a."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add files to the Collection List individually, using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and selecting them from a standard &kde; file dialog. You can "
"add entire folders using <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Folders "
"added this way will be rescanned every time you start &juk;. You can even "
"define folders inside these folders that will be excluded from scan. You can "
"force the folders to be rescanned by right-clicking on the "
"<guilabel>Collection List</guilabel> icon, and selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati datoteke listama kolekcija pojedinačno, koristeći "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otvori ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> i birajući ih iz standardog dijaloga &kde; "
"datoteke; Možete dodati kompletne foldere koristeći "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljaj "
"direktorijima...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Folderi dodani na ovaj način će "
"biti reskenirani svaki put kada pokrenete &juk; Čak možete definisati "
"foldere, koji će biti isključeni iz skeniranja, unutar ovih foldera. Možete "
"prouzrokovati reskeniranje foldera desnim klikom na <guilabel>Lista "
"kolekcija</guilabel> icon, i birajući <guimenuitem>Ponovo učitaj</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding a song to a playlist will automatically add its file to the "
"Collection List, but adding a file to the Collection List won't "
"automatically add the song to any playlists."
msgstr ""
"Dodavanje pjesme na muzičku listu će automatski dodati njen fajl u listu "
"kolekcija, ali dodavanje datoteke u listu kolekcija neće automatski dodati "
"pjesmu u muzičku listu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can quickly create a playlist from your entire Collection List, by &RMB; "
"clicking on the <guilabel>Collection List</guilabel> icon, and choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate</guimenuitem>. The resulting playlist is a normal "
"playlist, and editing it will not affect the <guilabel>Collection List</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Možete brzo kreirati muzičku listu iz vaše cijele Liste Kolekcija, koristeći "
"&RMB; kliom na <guilabel>Collection List</guilabel> icon, i izborom "
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate</guimenuitem>. Rezultujuća muzička lista je normalna "
"muzička lista, i njeno uređivajnje neće utjecati na  <guilabel>Collection "
"List</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add playlist files created outside &juk; individually by selecting "
"them with <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Any playlist files found in folders you add with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> will also be added automatically."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati datoteke iz muzičke liste kreirane izvan &juk;-a individualno "
"birajuči ih sa <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otvori ..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.  Svaka muzička lista pronađena u folderima koje "
"vi dodate sa <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljaj "
"Direktorijima...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>  će takođe biti dodana "
"automatski."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a new empty playlist, a search playlist or a playlist from a "
"folder by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> or the <guiicon>New</guiicon> icon on the toolbar. "
"You will be prompted for a name, and then an icon for that playlist will "
"appear in the playlist pane. You can now drag and drop files from the "
"Collection List, or from other playlists, to your playlist. Use the "
"<guiicon>Save</guiicon> icon or <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to save the playlist at "
"any time."
msgstr ""
"Možete kreirati novu praznu muzičku listu, pretragu liste ili muzičku listu "
"iz foldera birajući <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>  ili <guiicon>New</guiicon> ikoni na alatnoj "
"traci.  Bit će vam traženo ime, zatim će se ikona te liste pojaviti u okviru "
"liste. Sada možete ubaciti datoteke iz liste Kolekcija ili drugih listi u "
"vašu listu. Koristite <guiicon>Save</guiicon> ikonu ili "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Snimi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> da spremite vašu listu u bilo kojem trenutku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Song List"
msgstr "Lista pjesama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are viewing the Collection List, the main pane contains all the "
"files that &juk; knows about. When you are viewing a playlist, only the "
"songs that are in that playlist are shown. In either case, the appearance "
"and behavior of the list is the same."
msgstr ""
"Kada gledate listu kolekcija, prvi okvir sadrzi sve datoteke za koje &juk; "
"zna. Kada gledate listu muzičku listu, samo pjesme koje se nalaze u toj "
"listu su prikazane. U svakom slučaku izgled i ponašanje listi je isto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each song takes one row in the display. There is a column for each metadata "
"field that &juk; tracks. These columns correspond to the fields available to "
"edit in the tag editor."
msgstr ""
"Svaka pjesma zauzima jedan red na ekranu. Postoji kolona za svako polje "
"međupodataka koje &juk; prati. Ove kolone odgovaraju poljima slobodnim za "
"editovanje u editoru oznaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reorder the list at any time by &LMB; clicking on the column header. "
"This will first sort the files in ascending order based on the contents of "
"that column. If you &LMB; click again on the same header, the files will be "
"re-sorted in descending order."
msgstr ""
"Možete preurediti listu u svakom trenutku sa &LMB; klikom na zaglavlje "
"kolone. Ovo će prvo sortirati sve datoteke u rastućem redu zasnovanom na "
"sadržaju te kolone. Ako opet &LMB; kliknete na isto zaglavlje, datoteke će "
"biti resortirane u opadajućem redu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The columns are initially sized wide enough to show the longest entry "
"available. You can resize the columns by placing your mouse cursor on the "
"divider between two columns. When the cursor changes from a pointer, &LMB; "
"click and drag in the direction you want to resize the columns."
msgstr ""
"Inicijalna veličina kolona je dovoljno široka da prikaže najduži dostupan "
"unos. Možete promijeniti veličinu kolona postavljajući kursor miša na "
"djelitelj izmeđi dvije kolone. Kada se kursor promijeni od pokazivača, &LMB; "
"kliknite i povucite u smjeru u kojem želite promijeniti dimenziju kolone."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reorder the columns by &LMB; clicking on a header and dragging the "
"header to the left or right. You cannot drag past the edge of the window "
"when doing this however, so you may need to scroll a little to the left or "
"right, and repeat dragging the header, until you have placed it in your "
"preferred position."
msgstr ""
"Možete preurediti kolone sa &LMB; klikom na zaglavlje i povlačenjem "
"zaglavlja lijevo ili desno. Međutim, ne možete povući izvan ivica prozora "
"dok ovo radite, pa morate malo pomijerati lijevo ili desno, i ponoviti "
"povlačenje zaglavlje, dok ga ne smjestite u željenu poziciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can hide or unhide columns by &RMB; clicking on a column header, and "
"clicking on the name of the column to change."
msgstr ""
"Možete sakriti ili otkriti kolone sa &RMB; klikom na zaglavlje kolone, a "
"klikom na ime kolone za promjenu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&LMB; double clicking on a file will play it with the built-in player. If "
"another song was already playing, it will stop, and the new song will play."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; dupli klik na datoteku će je pokrenuti sa ugrađenim playerom Ako je "
"druga pjesma već pokrenuta, prestat će, a nova će se pokrenuti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "&RMB; clicking on a file offers you several options:"
msgstr "&RMB; klik na datoteku nudi vam nekoliko opcija:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Play Queue"
msgstr "Dodaj u red puštanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will start playing the file as soon as the current song is over. If no "
"song is playing, the file will be played when you next hit the "
"<guiicon>Play</guiicon> button. If you have already chosen the "
"<guimenuitem>Add to Play Queue</guimenuitem> option on a different file, "
"then this file will override that selection."
msgstr ""
"Ovo će pokrenuti datoteku čim trenutna pjesma bude završena. Ako nijedna "
"pjesma nije pokrenuta, tada će datoteka biti pokrenuta kada kliknete "
"<guiicon>Play</guiicon> dugme. Ako ste već odabrali  <guimenuitem>Add to "
"Play Queue</guimenuitem> opciju na neku drugu datoteku, tada će ovaa "
"datoteka nadglasati tu selekciju."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Isijeci</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Umetni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>...</para>"
msgstr "<para>...</para>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove from Playlist"
msgstr "Ukloni sa liste pjesama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are viewing the Collection List, choosing this action will remove the "
"file from the list, and will also remove all corresponding entries for this "
"song from all playlists. You should note that if this file is in a folder "
"that &juk; scans on startup, it will be readded to the Collection List the "
"next time you start up &juk; but it won't be automatically added to any "
"playlists."
msgstr ""
"Ako gledate listu kolekcija, izbor ove akcije će izbrisati datoteku iz "
"liste, i takođe će ukloniti sve odgovarajuće unose za ovu pjesmu iz svih "
"listi izvođenja. Trebate primijetiti da ako je ova datoteka u folderu u koji "
"&juk; skenira pri pokretanju, on će biti ponovo dodan u listu klekcija "
"sljedeci put kada pokrenete &juk; ali neće biti automatski dodan u listu "
"izvođenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are viewing a playlist, <guimenuitem>Remove from Playlist</"
"guimenuitem> will simply remove the song from the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ako gledate listu izvođenja, <guimenuitem>Ukloni iz liste izvođenja</"
"guimenuitem> će jednostavno ukloniti pjesmu iz liste izvođenja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit <replaceable>Column Title</replaceable>"
msgstr "Izmijeni <replaceable>Naslov kolone</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will allow you to edit the currently highlighted song, in the column you "
"clicked in. For example, if you do not have the tag editor visible, and you "
"are busy creating a playlist, but you notice a mis-spelling in an artist "
"name, you can edit it directly with this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Dozvolit će vam da izmijeniti trenutno označenu pjesmu, u koloni na koju ste "
"kliknuli. Naprimjer, ako nemate vidljiv editor oznaka, i zauzeti ste "
"kreiranjem liste izvođenja, ali primijetite pogrešno napisano ime izvđača "
"možete ga direktno izmijeniti sa ovom stavkom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes made in this manner are always saved immediately as soon as you "
"click elsewhere and are finished editing."
msgstr ""
"Promjene napravljene u ovom pogledu će uvijek biti spremljene trenutno čim "
"kliknete bilo gdje drugo i završeni ste sa izmjenama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item will be disabled if &juk; detects that the track you have "
"selected is read-only."
msgstr ""
"Ova stavka će biti onemogućena ako &juk; detektuje da je označena pjesma "
"samo za čitanje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Refresh"
msgstr "Osvježi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will reload the tag information of the selected files, in case the "
"files have been changed while &juk; was running."
msgstr ""
"Ovo će ponovo učitati informacije slektovanih datoteka, u slučaju da su "
"datoteke bile mijenjane dok je &juk; bio pokrenut."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Obriši"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will remove the file from the Collection List, remove all entries for "
"the song in all playlists, and delete the file from your disk. You cannot "
"undo this, although you will be asked to confirm your choice. Use this with "
"caution."
msgstr ""
"Ovo će ukloniti datoteku iz liste kolekcija, ukloniti sve unoste ove pjesme "
"u svim listama izvođenja i izbrisati datoteku sa vašeg diska. Ovo ne možete "
"poništiti, iako ćete biti pitani za potvrdu vašeg izbora. Koristite ovo sa "
"oprezom."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Guess Tag Information"
msgstr "Pogodite informaciju oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will make &juk; try to guess information such as the Artist and Title "
"of a song. &juk; employs different methods of guessing:"
msgstr ""
"Ovim će &juk; pokušati da pogodi informacije kao što su izvođač ili naziv "
"pjesme. &juk; koristi različite metode pogađanja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "From File Name"
msgstr "Iz imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try to guess the tags of the song based on its filename. For "
"example, a song name such as <filename>Roxette - You've Got the Look.mp3</"
"filename> would guess Roxette for the artist and You've Got the Look as the "
"title. You can adjust the way &juk; guesses for tags by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings </guimenu><guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which will open the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-"
"guesser-configuration\">Tag Guesser dialog</link>. &juk; will not replace "
"tags that it did not guess from the file name."
msgstr ""
"&juk;  će pokušati pogoditi pjesmu baziranu na njenom imenu datoteke. Na "
"primjer, za naziv pjesme kao što je <filename>Roxette - You've Got the Look."
"mp3</filename> će pogađati Roxette kao izvođač, a You've Got the Look kao "
"naslov. Možete prilagoditi način na koji &juk; pogađa oznake birajući  "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke </guimenu><guimenuitem>Pogađanje oznaka...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, što će otvoriti poveznicu <link linkend=\"juk-tag-"
"guesser-configuration\">Dijalog pogađanja oznaka</link>. &juk;  neće "
"zamijeniti oznake koje nije pogodio iz naziva datoteke."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "From Internet"
msgstr "Sa interneta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try to guess the tags of the song by using the MusicBrainz "
"program. You must have MusicBrainz installed for this command to work."
msgstr ""
"&juk; će pokušati da pogodi oznaku pjesme koristeći MusicBrainz program. "
"morate imati MusicBrainz instaliran da bi ova komanda radila."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename File"
msgstr "Preimenuj datoteku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will rename the selected files to conform to a given format. You must "
"choose the way you want the files renamed first by selecting <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Renamer...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. The resulting name of each file is based on its metadata tags. "
"For example, the Ogg Vorbis song <quote>The Theme (Metroid)</quote> by "
"Stemage could result in <filename>/usr/share/music/Stemage/The Theme "
"(Metroid).ogg</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Ovo će preimenovati odabrane datoteke da bi se prilagodile danom formatu. "
"Morate izabrati način na koji želite da datoteke budu preimenovane birajući "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenovanje "
"datoteke...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create Playlist From Selected Items"
msgstr "Kreiraj listu od odabranih datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to quickly create a playlist from songs in your Collection "
"List. This function will prompt you for a name for the new playlist, and "
"will then insert all of the songs that are selected into the new playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ovo vam omogućava da brzo kreirate listu od pjesama iz vaše liste kolekcija. "
"Ova funkcija će vam zatražiti ime nove liste, a zatim umetnuti sve označene "
"pjesme u novu listu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Selected Items to Audio or Data CD"
msgstr "Dodaj izabrane stavke na audio CD ili CD sa podacima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to quickly create a K3b &CD;-burning project from your "
"selected songs. &juk; will ask you if you would like an Audio &CD; project "
"or a Data &CD; project, unless K3b already has a project open."
msgstr ""
"Ovo vam omogućuje da brzo kreirate K3b &CD;-pisanje projekta od pjesama koje "
"ste odabrali. &juk; će vas pitati da li želite Audio &CD; projekat ili Data "
"&CD; projekat, osim ako K3b već ima otvoren projekat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If K3b is not already running, &juk; will start it up for you. After that, "
"&juk; will add your selected files to the current K3b project. You can then "
"save the project in K3b for burning later, or burn the &CD; right away."
msgstr ""
"Ako K3b nije već pokrenut, &juk; će ga pokrenuti za vas. Nakon toga, &uk; će "
"dodati vaše odabrane datoteke u trenutni K3b projekat. Tada možete spremiti "
"projekat u K3b za upisivanje kasnije, ili upisati na &CD; odmah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "&juk; Playlists"
msgstr "&juk; Lista izvođenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A playlist is simply a collection of songs grouped by some category. For "
"example, you may have a playlist of songs that you listen to while coding, "
"while trying to sleep, or even when you need a laugh. &juk; supports several "
"different types of playlists."
msgstr ""
"Lista izvođenja je jednostavno kolekcija pjesama grupisanih po nekoj "
"kateogriji. Na primjer, možete imati listu pjesama koje slušate dok "
"kodirate, dok pokušavate zaspati, ili čak kada trebate da se nasmijete. "
"&juk; podržava različite tipove listi numera."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal playlists"
msgstr "Normalna lista numera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most common kind of playlist. It is a playlist composed of "
"files, just like the Collection List."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je najčešća vrsta listi numera. To je lista sastavljena od datoteka, kao "
"u listama kolekcija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "The history playlist"
msgstr "Povijest liste numera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this playlist (by enabling <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show History</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, this playlist "
"will record every song that &juk; plays. The playlist will have an extra "
"column, <guilabel>Time</guilabel>, which records the exact time and date the "
"song played. The playlist doesn't start tracking the history until it is "
"enabled, however."
msgstr ""
"Ako omogućite ovu listu ( omogućavanjem <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži historiju</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ova lista "
"će snimiti svaku pjesmu koju &juk; pokrene. Ova lista će imati dodatnu "
"kolonu, <guilabel>Vrijeme</guilabel>, koja snima tačno vrijeme i datum kada "
"je pjesma pjevana. Međutim, ova lista ne pokreće praćenje historije, dok "
"nije omogućena."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search playlists"
msgstr "Traži listu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a playlist which is based off of a search. You can create a playlist "
"like this by clicking <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by "
"clicking on the <link linkend=\"juk-advanced-search-dialog\">Search "
"Playlist</link> button on the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je lista koja je bazirana na pretragi. Možete kreirati listu kao što je "
"ova klikom na <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ili "
"klikom na <link linkend=\"juk-advanced-search-dialog\">Traži listu numera</"
"link> dugme na alatnoj traci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After creating this playlist, it will keep track of which songs in the "
"Collection List match your criteria, and automatically update itself "
"accordingly whenever the Collection List changes."
msgstr ""
"Nakon kreiranja ove list, pratiće koje se pjesme u listi kolekcija "
"podudaraju sa vašim kriterijom, i automatski se ažurirati kad god se lista "
"kolekcija promijeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Playlists are organized in the <guilabel>Playlist pane</guilabel>, which is "
"the vertical bar at the left. In this pane is an icon for every playlist you "
"have. There are different view mode for this pane, which can be selected "
"from the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Liste su organizirane u <guilabel>Okvir liste numera</guilabel>, što je "
"vertikalna traka lijevo. U ovom okviru je ikona za svaku listu koju imate. "
"Različiti su načini pregledanja ovog okvira, koji mogu biti izabrani "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled načina</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> menija."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default View mode"
msgstr "Zadani način pregleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default view mode. In this mode, all the playlists are shown as "
"large icons, one above the other in the view mode."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je zadani način prikaza. U ovom modu, sve liste su prikazane kao velike "
"ikone, jedna iznad druge u načinu prikaza."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compact View mode"
msgstr "Kompaktan način prikaza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is similar to the Normal Viewmode, with the exception that the "
"playlists are represented with horizontal bars with small icons instead of "
"with square boxes."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj način je sličan normalnom načinu prikaza, sa izuzetkom da su liste "
"prikazane sa horizontalnih trakama sa malim ikonama umjesto sa kvadratima."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tree View mode"
msgstr "Stablo način prikaza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode is the most powerful. This mode is just like the Compact viewmode, "
"except that the Collection List is now the root of a tree of virtual "
"playlists. The Collection List has three children nodes, Artist, Album, and "
"Genre. Each of these node has children representing all of the entries from "
"that specific category. For example, if your Collection List contains music "
"from 4 different artists, you would have 4 entries under the artist node."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj način prikaza je najmoćniji. Ovaj način je kao kompaktni način prikaza, "
"sa izuzetkom da lista kolekcija koje je sada korijen stabla virtualnih "
"lista. Lista kolekcija ima tri čvora djece, Izvođač, Album i Žanr. Svaki od "
"ovih čvorova ima djete koje predstavlja sve unose specifične kategorije. Na "
"primjer, ako vaša lista kolekcija sadrži muziku 4 različita izvođača, imali "
"biste 4 unosa  ispod čvora izvođača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One nifty feature of the tree view mode is something called drag-and-drop "
"retagging. Simply select some files in the track list, and drag them onto "
"one of the artist, album, or genre nodes under Collection List. The songs "
"will automatically be retagged to match the item you dropped the tracks on. "
"For example, if you drag a group of tracks onto a Genre called \"Rock\", all "
"of the tracks will be retagged will a Genre tag of Rock."
msgstr ""
"Jedna od lijepih prednosti stabla je nešto nazvano povuci-i-ispusti "
"označavanje. Jednostavno izaberite neke datoteke iz liste pjesama, i "
"povucite ih do nekog čvora izvođača, albuma, ili žanra ispod lista kolekcija."
"Pjesme će automatski biti označene da se podudaraju sa stavkom na koje ste "
"ispustili pjesme. Naprimjer, ako povučete grupu pjesama na žanr zvan \"Rok"
"\", sve pjesme će biti označene oznakom žanra Rok."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &juk; Tag Editor"
msgstr "&juk; Editor oznaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For many file formats, it is practical to use the filename to describe the "
"contents of the file: <quote><filename>Report for the board - June 2003.doc</"
"filename></quote> for example, may be all the information you need in order "
"to find that file again. Trying to capture all the useful information about "
"a particular song however, could lead to filenames like this: "
"<quote><filename>Type O Negative - The Glorious Liberation Of The Peoples "
"Technocratic Republic Of Vinnland By The Combined Forces Of The United "
"Territories Of Europa.mp3</filename></quote> or <quote><filename>Various "
"Artists_15_The Smithsonian Collection of Classic Jazz Volume II_Jimmie "
"Lunceford &amp; His Orchestra - Organ Grinder's Swing.mp3</filename></"
"quote>. These are neither very practical to use, nor do they contain all of "
"the useful information that you might have collected about the song. Adding "
"the album, and track number, for example, to the first would make it even "
"longer and more unmanageable, while still not telling you at a glance the "
"year it was released, or what style of music it is, if you're not familiar "
"with the artist."
msgstr ""
"Za mnoge formate datoteka praktično je koristiti naziv datoteke koji opisuje "
"sadržaj datoteke. <quote><filename>Izvještaj za ploču - June 2003.doc</"
"filename></quote> naprimjer, mogu biti sve informacije koje trebate da biste "
"opet našli tu datoteku. Pokušavajući zabilježiti sve korisne informacije o "
"nekoj pjesmi može dovesti do imena datoteka kao ove <quote><filename>Type O "
"Negative - The Glorious Liberation Of The Peoples Technocratic Republic Of "
"Vinnland By The Combined Forces Of The United Territories Of Europa.mp3</"
"filename></quote> ili <quote><filename>Various Artists_15_The Smithsonian "
"Collection of Classic Jazz Volume II_Jimmie Lunceford &amp; His Orchestra - "
"Organ Grinder's Swing.mp3</filename></quote>.  Ovo nije praktično za "
"upotrebu , niti sadrže sve korisne informacije koje biste mogli imati o "
"pjesmi. Dodavanje albuma, broja pjesme naprimjer, prvoj riječi bi napravilo "
"ime čak i dužim i težim za upravljanje, a još uvijek vam ne bi govorilo o "
"godini kada je izdan ili koji je stil muzike, ako niste upoznati sa "
"izvođačem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The solution then, is to store this kind of metadata inside the files "
"themselves. Mp3 and ogg files can also contain small snippets of text which "
"you can use to describe the content of the file. There are several formats, "
"but &juk; hides the details of the differences between them, and provides a "
"standard way to edit a standard subset of well known tags for all your audio "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Rješenje je onda, das spremite ovu vrstu podataka unutar datoteka. Mp3 ili "
"ogg datoteka može takođe da sadrži dijelove tekstova koje mogu služiti da "
"opišu sadržaj datoteke. Postoji nekoliko formata, ali &juk; krije detalje o "
"razlikama između njih, i osigurava standardan način editovanja stadardnog "
"podskupa dobro poznatih oznaka za sve vaše audio datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk;'s full featured tag editor allows you to edit the tags in both mp3 and "
"ogg files. You can edit single files or multiple files, and you can select a "
"mix of mp3 and ogg files to edit. The only requirement is that you have "
"write access to the files themselves; you cannot edit the tags of a file "
"that is mounted from a &CD-ROM; for example."
msgstr ""
"&juk; je editor odznaka koji dozvoljava da editujete oznaka kako u vašim mp3 "
"tako i u ogg datotekama. Možete editovati pojedinačne datoteke ili grupu "
"datoteka, i možete odabrati mješavinu mp3 i ogg datoteka za editovanje. "
"Jedini zahtjev je da imate pristup pisanje na same datoteke; ne možete "
"editovati oznake na datoteci koja se nalazi na &CD-ROM;u naprimjer."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the Tags in a Single File"
msgstr "Editovanje tagova u jednoj datoteci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit the tag in a single file, select it in either the collection list or "
"any entries it has in any playlist. If the tag editor is not visible, enable "
"it by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag "
"Editor</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The tag editor displays in the bottom of "
"the list view."
msgstr ""
"Da biste editovali oznaku u pojedinačnoj datoteci,odaberite je ili iz liste "
"kolekcije ili iz bilo kog unosa koji se nalazi u bilo kojoj listi. Ako "
"editor oznaka nije vidljiv, omogućite to birajući "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži editor oznaka</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Editor oznaka će se prikazati na kraju prikaza "
"liste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply type into any of the editable fields to change the information. When "
"you are done, &LMB; click back in the list, and you will be prompted to save "
"your changes."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavno unesite bilo koji od polja koji se mogu izmijeniti da "
"promijenite informacije. Kada završite, &LMB; kliknite na kraj liste, i bit "
"će vam zatraženo spremanje promjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may find that the tag editor remains disabled when you've clicked on a "
"file. This happens when &juk; has detected that the track is read-only."
msgstr ""
"Možete primijetiti da editor oznaka može ostane onemogućen kada kliknete na "
"datoteku. Ovo se dešava kada &juk; detektuje da je pjesma samo za čitanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tag Editor Fields"
msgstr "Polja editora oznaka"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Artist Name:"
msgstr "Ime izvođača:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the Artist(s) who released the song."
msgstr "Ime izvođača koji je izdao pjesmu:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track name:"
msgstr "Naziv pjesme:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the song."
msgstr "Naziv pjesme."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "Album name:"
msgstr "Naziv albuma:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the album the song was released on."
msgstr "Naziv albuma pjesme sa kojeg je izdana."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Genre:"
msgstr "Žanr:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Style</quote> of the music. &juk; provides a list corresponding "
"roughly to the informal id3 standard, but you are free to type your own "
"entries in this list."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Stil</quote> muzike. &juk; obezbjeđuje listu koja odprilike odgovara "
"neformalnom id3 standradu, ali vam je dozvoljeno da pišete vlastite unose u "
"listu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "File name:"
msgstr "Naziv datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of the actual file on disk. You can edit this directly, and "
"when you save, the file will be renamed."
msgstr ""
"Naziv datoteke na disku. Možete ovo editovati direktno, i kada spremite, ime "
"datoteke će biti promijenjeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track:"
msgstr "Numera:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "The position of the track on the original recording."
msgstr "Pozicija numere na originalnom snimku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Year:"
msgstr "Godina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "The year the song was released."
msgstr "Godina izdavanja pjesme:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Length:"
msgstr "Dužina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523 index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is not editable, it is simply shown for information."
msgstr "Ovo nije moguće izmijeniti, prikazano je samo za informacije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bitrate:"
msgstr "Broj bitova:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comment:"
msgstr "Komentar:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add your own free text comment here, with additional notes &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati vaš vlastiti slobodni komentar, sa dodatnim bilješkama &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:543 index.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can explicitly and immediately save your changes at any time using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu entry or by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Možete ekspicitno i trenutačno spremiti promjene svaki put kada koristite  "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremi</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> unos na meniju ili ako pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing the Tags in Multiple Files"
msgstr "Editovanje oznaka u Višestrukim datotekama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select multiple files in the list view, and edit one or more fields "
"in the tags for all files at once."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati više datoteka u pregledniku liste i editovati jedno ili više "
"polja u oznakama za sve datoteke odjednom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use &Shift; and the &LMB; to select a contiguous list of files, and &Ctrl; "
"and &LMB; to select individual non-contiguous files."
msgstr ""
"Koristite &Shift; i &LMB; da odabere susjedne liste datoteke, i &Ctrl; i "
"&LMB; da odaberete individualne nesusjedne datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the tag editor is not visible, you can enable it by choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag Editor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The tag editor displays in the bottom of the list "
"view."
msgstr ""
"Ako editor oznaka nije vidljiv možete ga omogućiti birajući "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži editor oznaka</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Editor oznaka prikazuje se na kraju preglednika "
"liste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tag editor behaves slightly differently when you have selected multiple "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Editor oznaka se ponaša malo neznatno drugačije kada imate više selektovanih "
"datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each field in the tag editor will now show an <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> "
"check box next to it. Any field that has exactly the same contents for all "
"the files you selected, displays that content, and is enabled for editing, "
"with the <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> check box checked."
msgstr ""
"Svako polje u editoru oznaka će sada prikazati <guilabel>Omogući</guilabel> "
"kvadrat za označavanje pored njega. Svako polje koje ima potpuno isti "
"sadržaj za svaku datoteku koju odaberete, prikazuje taj sadržaj za "
"editovanje, sa <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> označenim kvadratom za "
"označavanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any field that does not have matching contents in all selected files is not "
"initially editable, and does not display any contents at all."
msgstr ""
"Svako polje koje nema odgovarajući sadržaj ni u jednom od selektovanih "
"datoteka nije inicijalno određen za editovanje i ne prikazuje nikakav "
"sadržaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the content of any field, check the <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> "
"check box if it is not already checked, and edit the field as you normally "
"would."
msgstr ""
"Da promijenite sadržaj bilo kojeg polja, označite <guilabel>Omogući</"
"guilabel> kućicu ako nije već označena, i izmijenite polje kao što bi i "
"inače."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done, &LMB; click back in the list view and you will be "
"prompted to save your changes. The prompt dialog will show you a list of the "
"affected files, so you have a chance to check that you are indeed altering "
"the files you intended to."
msgstr ""
"Kada završite, &LMB; kliknite nazad na pregled liste i bit će vam zatraženo "
"da spremite izmejene. Taj dijalog će vam prikazati listu datoteka na koje se "
"odnosi, tako da imate priliku da označite one fajlove koje ste zaista "
"željeli mijenjati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Rename File dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dijalog za mijenjanje imena datoteke</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Rename File dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dijalog za mijenjanje imena datoteke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Rename File dialog."
msgstr "Slika ekrana Dijaloga za mijenjanje imena datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The File Renamer Configuration dialog box is used to configure the Rename "
"File action, which renames a song's based on the information contained "
"within its metadata tags."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijski dijaloški prozor za promjenu imena dijaloga datoteke je "
"korišten da konfiguriše akciju promjene imena datoteke koji preimenuje "
"pjesmu baziranu na informaciji sadržanoj u njenoj oznaci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The whole Rename File feature is used to get consistent file names for your "
"music collection (including moving the files if necessary). For example you "
"may have some songs which appear on disk as <filename>01 - Title.mp3</"
"filename> if you got them from <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com\">Amazon</"
"ulink>, while songs from <ulink url=\"http://ocremix.org/\">OCRemix</ulink> "
"might be <filename>Ailsean- Mega_Man_3_Mega_Fire_(OC_Remix).mp3</filename> "
"or something along those lines."
msgstr ""
"Svojsto preimenovanja datoteke je korišteno za dobijanje konzistentnih imena "
"fajlova vaših muzičkih kolekcija (uključujući filmove ako je potrebno). Na "
"primjer možete imati pjesme koje se prikazuju na disku kao <filename>01 - "
"naziv.mp3</filename> ako ste ih dobili iz <ulink url=\"http://amazon.com"
"\">Amazon</ulink>, dok pjesme <ulink url=\"http://ocremix.org/\">OCRemix</"
"ulink> mogu biti <filename>Ailsean- Mega_Man_3_Mega_Fire_(OC_Remix).mp3</"
"filename> ili nešto uz ove linije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the file renamer allows &juk; to rename those songs to something "
"<quote>sane</quote> on-disk, such as <filename>Ailsean - Mega Fire.mp3</"
"filename> and <filename>The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</filename>. You can even "
"include paths throughout to automatically sort the music (&eg; by year or "
"album), like <filename>$HOME/Music/2003/The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Korištenje preimenovanja datoteka dozvoljava &juk; u da preimenuje pjesme u "
"nešto <quote>sane</quote> na disku, kao što je <filename>Ailsean - Mega Fire."
"mp3</filename> i <filename>The Strokes - Reptilia.mp3</filename>. Možete "
"takođe uključiti put kroz koji možete automatski sortirati muziku (&eg; po "
"godini ili albumu), kao <filename>$HOME/Music/2003/The Strokes - Reptilia."
"mp3</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Doing this is as simple as activating the <quote>Rename File</quote> action, "
"either from the <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu> menu, or right-clicking on the "
"files. The default is the <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> "
"shortcut. But before this is done you should setup how the files are to be "
"renamed."
msgstr ""
"Raditi ovo je jednako jednostavno kao aktiviranje akcije <quote>Preimenuj "
"datoteku</quote> , iz <guimenu>Tager</guimenu> menija, ili desnim klikom na "
"fajlove. Zadana prečica je  <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> . "
"Ali prije nego što je ovo urađeno trebali biste postaviti kako će se fajlovi "
"preimenovati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That is done from the above mentioned dialog that can be opened with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>File Renamer...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. You can define a destination path, by "
"using a base music folder and then adding pieces to there. These path pieces "
"would be based on the music metadata such as song title, artist, &etc;, and "
"are added using the <guilabel>Add Category</guilabel> selector."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se radi iz gore spomenutog dijaloga koji može biti otvoren sa "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenuj fajl...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Možete definisati odredišni put koristeći bazni "
"folder muzike i dodavanjem dijelova tu. Ovo dijelovi puta bili bi bazirani "
"na međupodacima muzike kao što su naziv, izvođač pjesme, &etc; i dodavani "
"korištenjem <guilabel>Dodaj kategoriju</guilabel>  selektora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each \"path piece\" has a check box between it allowing a folder separator "
"to be added."
msgstr ""
"Između svakog \"dijela puta\" je kutija za označavanje dozvoljavaljući "
"separatoru foldera da bude dodan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options for each piece, which simply control what happens if the "
"appropriate metadata is empty, and allow a prefix/suffix when the entry is "
"substituted in, can help you to make the renaming procedure more effective."
msgstr ""
"Opcije za svaki dio, koje jednostavno kontroliraju šta se dešava ako je "
"odgovarajući metapodatak prazan, i dozvoljavaju prefikse/sufikse kada je "
"unos zamijenjen, može vam pomoći da ostatak procedure bude efikasniji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Konfiguracijiski djialog pogađanja oznaka</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracijiski djialog pogađanja oznaka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Tag Guesser Configuration dialog."
msgstr "Slika ekrana kofiguracijskog dijaloga pogađanja oznaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Tag Guesser Configuration dialog is used to configure the "
"<guilabel>Guess from File Name</guilabel> action."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijski dijalog pogađanja oznaka se koristi da konfiguriše "
"<guilabel>Pogodi iz imena datoteke</guilabel> akciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dialog you will see a list on the left of different filename scheme "
"patterns. &juk; includes an extensive set of defaults patterns to match most "
"common filenaming styles. If you'd like to add a new scheme, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> button, and type in your scheme and click on "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"U dijalogu vidjet ćete listu različitih šema uzoraka imena dototeka lijevo. "
"&juk; uključuje obiman skup zadanih uzoraka koji odgovaraju najčešćim "
"stilovima imenovanja datoteka. Ako biste željeli dodati novu šemu, kliknite "
"na <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> \n"
"dugme i unesite vašu šemu , pa kliknite na <guibutton>OK</guibutton> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can see the currently configured file name schemes which the tag "
"editor uses to extract tag information from a file name. Each string may "
"contain one of the following placeholders:"
msgstr ""
"Ovdje možete pogledati trenutno konfigurisana imena đema koje editor oznaka "
"koristi da ekstraktuje oznaku informacije iz imena datoteke. Svaki string "
"može da sadrži jednu od sljedećih rezervisanih mjesta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid "%t: Title"
msgstr "%t: Naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "%A: Album"
msgstr "%A: Album"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "%a: Artist"
msgstr "%a: Izvođač"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "%T: Track"
msgstr "%T: Numera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "%c: Comment"
msgstr "%c: Komentar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, the file name scheme <quote>[%T] %a - %t</quote> would match "
"<quote>[01] Deep Purple - Smoke on the water</quote> but not <quote>(Deep "
"Purple) Smoke on the water</quote>. For that second name, you would use the "
"scheme <quote>(%a) %t</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Na primjer, šema imena datoteke  <quote>[%T] %a - %t</quote> bi odgovarala "
"<quote>[01] Deep Purple - Smoke on the water</quote> ali ne <quote>(Deep "
"Purple) Smoke on the water</quote>. Za to drugo ime, koristili biste šemu "
"<quote>(%a) %t</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&juk; will try the schemes you have listed one at a time, starting at the "
"top of the list. The first scheme which results in a match will be the "
"scheme used to guess the song's tags. Some songs may match more than one "
"scheme. You can make sure that the correct scheme matches first by selecting "
"the scheme in the list box and then using the arrow buttons to move it to "
"the top of the list."
msgstr ""
"&juk; će probati sve šeme koje ste naveli jednu po jednu, počevši od prve na "
"listi. Prva šema koja bude odgovarala će biti korištena za pogađanje oznaka "
"pjesme. Neke pjesme mogu odgovarati više od jednoj šemi. Mođete biti sigurni "
"da će se tačna šema uklopiti prva selektovanjem šeme na lista kutiji a onda "
"korištenjem tipki sa strelicama pomjeriti ih na vrh liste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also edit or remove a scheme from the list. Just select the scheme "
"in the list, and use the <guibutton>Modify</guibutton> button to change the "
"scheme, or the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button to remove the scheme "
"from the list."
msgstr ""
"Možete takođe urediti ili izbrisati šemu iz liste. Samo odaberite šemu na "
"listi i koristite  <guibutton>Izmijeni</guibutton> dugme da promijenite "
"šemu, ili <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> dugme da je izbrišete sa liste."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The Advanced Search dialog</title>"
msgstr "<title>Dijalog naprednog pretraživanja</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Advanced Search dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>The Advanced Search dialog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Advanced Search Dialog."
msgstr "Slika ekrana Dijaloga naprednog pretraživanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Advanced Search dialog is used to create <link linkend=\"juk-search-"
"playlists\">Search Playlists</link>. It allows you to make a fine-grained "
"search among the different tags of your song collection."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog naprednog pretraživanja se koristi da se kreira  <link linkend=\"juk-"
"search-playlists\">Pretraži Liste numera</link>.  On dozvoljava da napravite "
"finu pretragu između različitih oznaka vaše kolekcije pjesama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of the dialog, you can type in the name of your search playlist. "
"Then, you can define your search criteria in the <guilabel>Search Criteria</"
"guilabel> group."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu dijaloga, možete unijeti ime vaše liste za pretragu. Onda, mođete "
"definisati kriterij pretrage u <guilabel>Pretraži po kriteriju</guilabel> "
"grupi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top of the <guilabel>Search Criteria</guilabel> group has two radio "
"buttons, <guilabel>Match any of the following</guilabel> and <guilabel>Match "
"all of the following</guilabel>. If you select <guilabel>Match any of the "
"following</guilabel>, then a match by any of the conditions you define will "
"include the song in the playlist. Otherwise, every condition you define must "
"match in order to include the song in the playlist."
msgstr ""
"Vrh <guilabel>Pretraži po kriteriju</guilabel> grupe ima dva radio dugmeta, "
"<guilabel>Spoji bilo koji od navedenih</guilabel> i <guilabel>Spoji sve od "
"navedenih</guilabel>. Ako izaberete <guilabel>Spoji bilo koji od navedenih</"
"guilabel>, tada će podudaranje sa bilo kojim od uslova koji navedete "
"uključiti pjesmu u listu numera. U drugom slučaju, svaki uvjet koji "
"definišete mora da se podudara da bi se pjesma uključila u listu numera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the radio buttons are the condition definitions. You can add more "
"conditions by using the <guibutton>More</guibutton> button, and remove "
"conditions by using the <guibutton>Fewer</guibutton> button. Any conditions "
"you leave blank are ignored, so you do not have to use <guibutton>Fewer</"
"guibutton> to eliminate empty conditions."
msgstr ""
"Ispod radio dugmeta su definicije uvjeta. Možete dodati još uvjeta koristeći "
"<guibutton>Više</guibutton> dugme, i izbrisati uslove koristeći "
"<guibutton>Manje</guibutton> dugme. Svaki uvjet koji ostavite prazan će biti "
"ignorisan, pa ne morate koristiti <guibutton>Manje</guibutton> da "
"eliminišete prazne uslove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:751
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every condition definition has three parts: The tag chooser list on the "
"left, the matching style list on the right, and the search text in the "
"middle. The tag chooser lets &juk; know what tag you want to search for the "
"text in. If you choose the special tag \"&lt;All Visible&gt;\", then any tag "
"that you can see in the Collection List listing is fair game to match the "
"search text."
msgstr ""
"Svaka definicija uvjeta ima tri dijela: Lista birača:Izbronik oznaka liste "
"lijevo,  stil podudranja liste desno, i pretraga teksta u sredini. Izbornik "
"oznaka dozvoljava &juk;u da zna koju oznaku želite tražiti za tekst unutra. "
"Ako odaberete specijalan tag \"&lt;Sve vidljivo&gt;\", tada svaka oznaka "
"koju mođete vidjeti u listingu liste kolekcija je jednako moguća za "
"podudaranje sa tekstom pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The match style list lets &juk; know which search method to use. The search "
"methods you can use are as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Poklapanje stila liste dopušta &juk;u da zna koji metod pretrage da koristi. "
"Metode pretrage koje možete koristiti su:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Matching"
msgstr "Normalno poklapanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default matching style. It searches for the given text anywhere "
"in the chosen tag, ignoring case differences. For example a search for mode "
"in the Artist tag would match Depeche Mode."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je zadani stil poklapanja. On pretrađuje dati tekst svuda u izabranom "
"tagu, ignorišući razlike velikih i malih slova. Naprimjer traženjem mode u "
"tagu izvođača bi pronašla Depeche Mode."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case Sensitive"
msgstr "Razlikovanje malih i velikih slova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This search is just like Normal Matching, except that the search must match "
"the exact case of the text."
msgstr ""
"Ova pretraga je kao normalno poklapanje, sa izuzetkom da pretraga mora tačno "
"razlikovati velika i mala slova teksta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pattern Matching"
msgstr "Poklapanje uzorka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most powerful search method. The search text you type in will "
"define a regular expression used to search within the tag. Regular "
"expressions are beyond the scope of this documentation, but the application "
"&kregexpeditor; can help you form a regular expression. &juk; uses the &Qt; "
"regular expression style."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je najmoćniji metod pretrage. Tekst koji unesete će definisati regularni "
"izraz korišten za pretragu unutar oznake. Regularni izrazi su izvan opsega "
"ove dokumentacije ali aplikacija &kregexpeditor;  vam može pomoći da "
"kreirate regularan izraz. &juk; uses the &Qt; stil regularnog izraza."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply choose the conditions you want to include in your search, and click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to create your search playlist!"
msgstr ""
"Jednostavno odaberite uslove koje želite uključiti u vašu pretragu i "
"kliknite <guibutton>U redu</guibutton> da kreirate vašu listu za pretragu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &juk; Toolbar"
msgstr "The &juk; Alatna traka"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Toolbar"
msgstr "Glavna alatna traka"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &juk; toolbar.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&juk; alatna traka.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &juk; toolbar.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&juk; alatna traka.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The &juk; toolbar.</para>"
msgstr "<para>&juk; alatna traka.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From left to right in the screenshot above, the icons on the default toolbar "
"are:"
msgstr "Lijevo ka desno u slici ekrana iznad, ikone zadane alatne trake su:"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>New</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Novi</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new playlist. If you hold down the button, a menu will pop up "
"allowing you to select the different kinds of playlists to create."
msgstr ""
"Kreirajte novu listu numera. Ako držite pritisnuto dugme, meni će iskočiti "
"dozvoljavajući vam da odaberete vrste listi za kreiranje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empty Playlist..."
msgstr "Prazna lista numera..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This prompts you for a playlist name, and then inserts it into the Playlist "
"view. The playlist starts out completely empty."
msgstr ""
"Ovo vam traži ime liste numera, a onda je ubacuje u preglednik Listi numera. "
"Lista je na početku potpuno prazna."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playlist From Folder..."
msgstr "Liste numera iz foldera..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This prompts you for a folder to open, and then creates a playlist "
"containing the music within the folder and any sub-folders. The name of the "
"created playlist is the same as the name of the selected folder."
msgstr ""
"Ovo vam traži folder za otvaranje, a onda kerira listu numera koja sadrži "
"muziku iz foldera i bilo kojeg pod-foldera. Ime kreirane liste je isto kao i "
"ime odabranog foldera."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Playlist..."
msgstr "Pretraži listu numera..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This brings up the Advanced Search Dialog, allowing you to create a "
"<quote>virtual playlist</quote>. Any songs in your Collection List that "
"match the search criteria that you specify in the Advanced Search Dialog "
"will be added to the new playlist. As your Collection List changes, the new "
"playlist will as well. For example, if you create a playlist of all of your "
"Depeche Mode songs, and then add another Depeche Mode song to your "
"Collection List, it will show up in the Depeche Mode playlist with no "
"special action required on your part."
msgstr ""
"Ovo otvara Dijalog napredne pretrage, dozvoljavajući vam da kerirate "
"<quote>virtualnu listu</quote>. Bilo koja pjesma iz Liste kolekcija koja se "
"poklapa sa kriterijom pretrage koji ste specificirali u Dijalogu napredne "
"pretrage će biti dodana u novu listu. Ako se Lista kolekcija promijeni, "
"promijenit će se i nova lista numera. Naprimjer, ako kreirate listu svih "
"vaših pjesama Depeche Mode-a, i ona dodate drugu pjesmu Depeche Mode-a u "
"vašu listu kolekcija, ona će se pojavati u listi numera Depeche Mode-a bez "
"ikakve potrebne akcije sa vaše strane."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open"
msgstr "Otvori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add a file to the collection list (if it's active) or to the currently "
"selected playlist. Adding a file to a playlist will add it to the collection "
"list automatically, but not vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj datoteku listi kolekcija ( ako je aktivna ) ili trenutno selektovanoj "
"listi. Dodavanje datoteke listi će je dodati listi kolekcija automatski, ali "
"ne i obratno."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Sačuvaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the currently selected playlist. To save a tag you have edited, either "
"select another item, or press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</"
"keycap></keycombo> instead."
msgstr ""
"Sačuvaj trenutno odabaranu listu. Da biste spremili oznake koje ste "
"editovali, odaberite neku drugu stavku, ili umjesto toga pritisnite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Cut</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Isijeci</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a playlist or song is selected, cut (remove) it from the list. If the tag "
"editor is active, this works like cut in any editor, removing the selected "
"text, but keeping a copy on the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Ako je lista pjesama ili pjesma selektovana, isijeci (ukloni) je sa liste. "
"Ako je editor oznaka aktivan, ovo radi kao isijeci u bilo kojem editoru, "
"uklanjajući odabrani tekst, ali zadržavajući kopiju na spremniku."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Copy</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Kopiraj</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the tag editor is active, this works like copy in any editor, placing a "
"copy of the selected text on the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Ako je editor oznaka aktivan, ovo radi kao kopiranje u bilo kojem editoru, "
"stavljajući kopiju odabranog teksta na spremnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use copy on a song in the collection list, the url is placed on the "
"clipboard, so you can paste it. For example, you could paste the url into a "
"text editor, &konqueror;, or another playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ak koristite kopiranje na pjesmi u listi kolekcija, url je postavljen na "
"spremnik, pa ga možete umetnuti. Naprimjer, mogli biste umetnuti url u tekst "
"editor, &konqueror;, ili drugu listu."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guiicon>Paste</guiicon>"
msgstr "<guiicon>Umetni</guiicon>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you previously either cut or copied a url from the collection list, you "
"can paste the url back into a new playlist. You could also paste a url you "
"have copied from &konqueror; or any other application. If you are operating "
"in the tag editor, paste will paste any text currently on the clipboard into "
"the selected field."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste prethodno ili isijekli ili kopirali url iz liste kolekcija, možete "
"umetnuti url nazad u novu listu. Možete takođe umetnuti url koji ste "
"kopirali iz &konqueror; ili bilo koje druge aplikacije. Ako ste aktivni u "
"editoru oznaka, umetni će umetnuti trenutni tekst u spremniku u odabrano "
"polje."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Search Bar"
msgstr "Prikazi traku za pretragu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show or hide <link linkend=\"search-bar\">the search bar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži ili sakrij <link linkend=\"search-bar\">traku za pretragu</link>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Tag Editor"
msgstr "Prikaži editor oznaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show or hide <link linkend=\"tagging-a-single-file\">the tag editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži ili sakrij <link linkend=\"tagging-a-single-file\">editor oznaka</"
"link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Play controls"
msgstr "Kontrole pokretanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These work like any standard media player you may have come across. The "
"controls are <guiicon>Play</guiicon>, <guiicon>Pause</guiicon>, "
"<guiicon>Stop</guiicon>, <guiicon>Previous </guiicon> and <guiicon>Next</"
"guiicon>."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se koristi kao standardni plejer medija sa kojima ste se susretali. "
"Kontrole su <guiicon>Pokreni</guiicon>, <guiicon>Pauziraj</guiicon>, "
"<guiicon>Zaustavi</guiicon>, <guiicon>Prethodna</guiicon> i "
"<guiicon>Sljedeća</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a tracking bar, showing how far along (relatively) in the "
"current song you are. You can drag this slider with the mouse in order to "
"skip forwards or backwards within a track."
msgstr ""
"Takođe postoji traka za praćenje, koja pokazuje koliko dugo (relativno) "
"slušate pjesmu. Možete povući klizač sa mišem da biste ubrazli ili usporili "
"pjesmu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally there is a volume slider. As you may expect, this raises and lowers "
"the volume. <quote>Loud</quote> is on the right, and <quote>Quiet</quote> is "
"on the left."
msgstr ""
"Napokon tu je klizač za jačinu zvuka. Kao što možete očekivati, ovo "
"povećava ,odnosno smanjuje jačinu zvuka. <quote>Glasno</quote> je desno, a "
"<quote>Tiho</quote>je lijevo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1009
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Search bar"
msgstr "Traka za pretragu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search bar allows you to quickly search for a song in the collection "
"list or a playlist."
msgstr ""
"Traka za pretragu dozvoljava vam brzo traženje pjesme u listi kolekcija ili "
"listi numera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1014
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply typing text into the search bar will reduce the visible list of songs "
"to those which contain that text in any visible column. Pressing &Enter; "
"will start playing the top match in the playlist view."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavan unos teksta u traku pretrage će reducirati listu pjesama na onu "
"koja sadrži uneseni tekst u bilo kojoj vidljivoj koloni. Pritiskanjem "
"&Enter; pokrenut će se prva pjesma na vrhu liste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching begins instantly when text is entered into the search field. "
"Searching is incremental, that is, as you type each character into the text "
"field, the search is narrowed further. This is useful to find a song where "
"you only remember part of a name, for instance."
msgstr ""
"Pretraga počinje onog trenutka kada je tekst unesen u polje za pretragu. "
"Pretraga je inkrementalna, to jest, rezultati pretrage se sužavaju kako "
"unosite karaktere u polje. Ovo je korisno kada se sjećate samo dijela "
"pjesme, naprimjer."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu and Command Reference"
msgstr "Meni i naredbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus"
msgstr "Meniji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Menu"
msgstr "Meni datoteke"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Empty Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Prazna lista numera...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new playlist"
msgstr "Napravi novu listu pjesama"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Search Playlist...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Lista pretrage...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new <link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\">search playlist</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kreira novu <link linkend=\"juk-search-playlists\">listu pretrage</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Playlist From Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nova</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Lista iz foldera...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new playlist, containing all music files in a folder and any sub-"
"folders. Any music within playlists files that &juk; recognizes will also be "
"added."
msgstr ""
"Kreira novu listu numera, koja sadrži sve muzičke datoteke iz foldera i bilo "
"kojeg pod-foldera. Sva muzika unutar lista koju &juk; prepozaje će takođe "
"biti dodana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Otvori...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a file (or files) to add to the collection list. If you select a "
"playlist file, every file in the playlist will be added."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite datoteku (ili datoteke) koje želite dodati listi kolekcija. Ako "
"odaberete listu, svaka datoteka u toj listi će biti dodana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Folders...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljaj folderima...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens the same window that is shown on a first &juk; start"
msgstr "Ova stavka menija otvara isti prozor koji se prikazuje na &juk; startu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select a folder (or folders) to add to the collection list. These folders "
"will also be rescanned whenever &juk; is started or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> is chosen."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite folder (ili foldere) koje želite dodati listi kolekcija. Ovi "
"folderi će biti reskenirani kad god je &juk; pokrenut ili "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovo pokreni</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> je odabaran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select folders that should not be automatically searched (which "
"would override the list of folders to scan on startup). This way you can "
"avoid having to completely change up your music layout on-disk just to keep "
"&juk; from automatically grabbing songs you do not want or need managed from "
"within &juk;."
msgstr ""
"Možete takođe odabrati foldere koji ne bi trebali biti automatski pretraženi "
"( što bi preklopilo listu foldera za sekniranje pri pokretanju ). Na ovaj "
"način možete da izbejgnete kompletno mijenjanje rasporeda muzike na disku "
"samo da biste spriječili &juk; da automatski ugrabi pjesme koje ne želite "
"ili ne trebate da budu upravljane iz &juk;-a."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1116
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Manage Folders dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog Upravljanja Folderima"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Manage Folders Dialog."
msgstr "Slika ekrana dijaloga Upravljanja Folderima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to remove files that are already in the collection list, you can "
"enable the <guilabel>File Name (full path)</guilabel> column in a playlist "
"and then use the search bar to find the offending path name, select and "
"remove the files that are shown."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite ukloniti datoteke koji su već u listi kolekcija možete omogučiti "
"<guilabel>Ime datoteke (cijeli put)</guilabel> kolonu u listi numera i onda "
"koristiti traku za pretragu da pronađete problematičnog puta, selektujete i "
"uklonite prikazane datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rename...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenuj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename a playlist."
msgstr "Preimenuj listu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Duplicate...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uduplaj...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a duplicate of the selected playlist, and prompt for a new name."
msgstr "Kreira duplikaciju selektovane liste numera, i traži novo ime."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovo učitaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reloads the tag information on every file in the selected playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ponovo učitava informacije u oznakama na svakoj datoteci selektovane liste."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ukloni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the selected playlist."
msgstr "Ukloni selektovanu listu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist."
msgstr "Spremi selektovanu listu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Snimi kao...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save the selected playlist, with a different name."
msgstr "Spremi selektovanu listu, pod drugim imenom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Izmijeni meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Izmijeni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected songs from the playlist."
msgstr "Uklanja selektovane pjesme iz lise numera."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Prikaz Meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Search Bar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži traku pretrage</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"search-"
"bar\">Search Bar</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je akcija koja se postavlja u zavisnosti da li jeste  ili nije <link "
"linkend=\"search-bar\">Traka pretrage</link> prikazana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Tag Editor</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži editor oznaka</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <interface>Tag Editor</"
"interface> is shown."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je akcija koja se postavlja u zavisnosti da li jeste  ili nije "
"<interface>Editor oznaka</interface> prikazan."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show History</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži historiju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle action that sets whether or not the <link linkend=\"juk-"
"history-playlists\">History Playlist</link> is shown."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je akcija koja  se postavlja u zavisnosti da li jeste ili nije <link "
"linkend=\"juk-history-playlists\">Historija liste numera</link> prikazana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Default</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikaz načina</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Zadano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\">Default View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Mijenja u  <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-default\">Zadani način prikaza</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Compact</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Prikaz</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikaz načina</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Kompaktno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\">Compact View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Mijenja u <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-compact\">Kompaktni način prikaza</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>View Modes</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Tree</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Prikaz načina</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Stablo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches to <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\">Tree View mode</link>."
msgstr ""
"Mijenja u <link linkend=\"juk-viewmode-tree\">Stablo način prikaza</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player Menu"
msgstr "Plejer izbornik"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Random Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Plejer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Slučajno pokretanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Random Play setting. If Random "
"Play is enabled, then &juk; will randomly select a random song from the "
"current playlist when the currently playing song is over."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je opcija koja kontroliše postavku slučajnog pokretanja. Ako je Slučajno "
"Pokretanje omogučeno, tada &juk; nasumice odabira slučajnu pjesmu iz "
"trenutne liste kada se trenutno pokrenuta pjesma završi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Loop Playlist</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Petlja lista</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option which controls the Loop Playlist setting. If Loop "
"Playlist is enabled, then &juk; will start playing from the beginning when "
"it has finished playing every song in the current playlist."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je opcija koja kontroliše postavku Petlje liste. Ako je Petlja liste je "
"omogućena, tada &juk; počinje ponovo kreće od početka kada je završena svaka "
"pjesma u trenutnoj listi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokreni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command starts playing the currently selected song, or resumes playback "
"of the song if it was paused."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda pokreće trenutno selektovanu listu, ili nastavlja pjesmu ako je "
"bila pauzirana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pause</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pauza</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command pauses the currently playing song. Use the Play command to "
"restart playback."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda pauzira trenutno pokrenutu pjesmu. Koristite Pokreni komandu da "
"restartujete matricu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejerr</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaustavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command stops the playback of the currently playing song. You cannot "
"resume playback from its current position after that."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda zaustavlja matricu od trenutno pokrenute pjesme. Ne možete "
"nastaviti matricu iz njene trenutne pozicije nakon toga."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sljedeća</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command skips to the next song to play in the playlist."
msgstr "Ovom komandom preskačete do sljedeće pjesme u listi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Player</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Plejerr</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prethodna</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command plays the song that was playing before the currently playing "
"song."
msgstr ""
"Ova pjesma pokreće pjesmu koja je bila pokrenuta prije trenutne pjesme."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1369
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagger Menu"
msgstr "Tager meni"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command saves any changes to the tags that you are editing. Normally, "
"changes are not saved until you deselect the file you are editing."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda sprema sve promjene na oznakama koje uređujete. Naravno, "
"promjene nisu spremljene sve dok ne odznačite datoteku koju uređujete."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the currently selected files from the Collection List "
"and any playlists containing it, and then deletes the selected file from the "
"disk."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda briše trenutno označene datoteke iz Liste Kolekcija i svake "
"liste koju ona sadrži, i briše selektovane datoteke sa diska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Tagerr</guimenu><guimenuitem>Osvježi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command allows you to refresh playlist tags after changing them."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda vam dozvoljava da osvježite oznake liste nakon što ih izmijenite."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Filename</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogodite tag informacija</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Iz Naziva fajla</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by scanning the "
"filename. You can configure the patterns used for guessing by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which opens the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-"
"configuration\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda pokušava da pogodi oznake selektovanih fajlova skenirajući ime "
"datoteke. Možete konfigurisati korištene uzorke za pogađanje selektujući "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pogađač oznaka..</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guisubmenu>Guess Tag Information</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>From Internet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogodi tag informacija</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sa interneta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command tries to guess the tags of the selected files by using the "
"<application>TunePimp</application> library provided with <ulink url="
"\"http://www.musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda pokušava da pogodi tagove selektovanih datoteka koristeći  "
"<application>TunePimp</application> biblioteku obezbjeđenu sa<ulink url="
"\"http://www.musicbrainz.org/\">MusicBrainz</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tagger</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rename File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tager</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preimenuj datoteku</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command allows you to rename a file or a group of files for the "
"selected songs in the playlist. Before the real rename happens &juk; will "
"show a preview dialog where you can confirm or cancel the action."
msgstr ""
"Ova vam komanda dozvoljava da preimenujete datoteku ili grupu datoteka "
"selektovane pjesme liste. Prije nego se preimenovanje zaista dogodi &juk; će "
"vam prikazati dijalog gdje možete potvrditi akciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The files will be renamed according to the parameters defined using <link "
"linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">Rename File dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ove datoteke će biti preimenovane prema parametrima definisanim koristeći "
"<link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">Dijalog Preimenuj datoteku </link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni Postavki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Toolbars Shown</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Main / Play Toolbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu><guisubmenu>Alatne trake prikazane</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Osnovna / Pokreni alatna traka</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These commands show or hide the <link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Main Toolbar</"
"link> and the <link linkend=\"play-toolbar\">Play Toolbar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ove komanda pokazuju ili sakrivaju <link linkend=\"main-toolbar\">Osnovna "
"alatna traka</link>  i   <link linkend=\"play-toolbar\">Pokreni alatna "
"traka</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dok u Sistemskom izborniku</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an icon in your "
"system tray. You can use the system tray icon to tell if &juk; is playing, "
"and control playback."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je uključi/isključi opcija. Ako je uključena, &juk; če prikazati ikonu u "
"vašem sistemskom izborniku. Možete koristiti ikonu u sistemskom izborniku da "
"znate da li je &juk; pokrenuo pjesmu, i kontrolisati matricu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stay in System Tray on Close</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zadrži u Sistemskom izborniku pri "
"zatvaranju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will remain running if you close "
"the main window. The <guimenuitem>Dock in System Tray</guimenuitem> option "
"must also be enabled. To quit &juk;, use the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> command from the main "
"window, or the <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem> command from the system "
"tray's context menu."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je uključi/isključi opcija. Ako je uključena, &juk; će ostati pokrenut "
"ako zatovrite glavni prozor. <guimenuitem> Usidri u sistemskom uglu</"
"guimenuitem> opcija takođe mora biti uključena. Da zatvorite &juk; koristite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zatvori</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>  komandu iz glavnog prozora, ili  <guimenuitem>Zatvori</"
"guimenuitem> komandu iz kontekst menija sistemskog izbornika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &juk; is started up when it is set to dock in the system tray on startup "
"a simple notification will be shown (as otherwise the user may wonder why "
"&juk; window did not open up). It is possible to remove this additional "
"notification by going to <menuchoice><guimenu>Common Appearance and "
"Behavior</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Application and System Notifications</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &systemsettings; to manage <guilabel>JuK music "
"player</guilabel> application notifications. Just uncheck <guilabel>Show a "
"message in a popup</guilabel> item for <guimenuitem>JuK running in dock "
"mode</guimenuitem>. More information on &kde; notification settings can be "
"found <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ako je &juk; pokrenut kada je postavljen na dok u sistemskom izborniku, pri "
"pokretanju će biti prikazana jednostavna notifikacija ( u drugom slučaju "
"korisnik bi se mogao zapitati zašto se prozor &juk;-a nije otvorio). Moguće "
"je izbrisati ovu dodatnu notifikaciju idući na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Zajednički izgled i ponašanje</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Aplikacijske i sistemske notifikacije</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> u &systemsettings; da upravljate <guilabel>JuK uzički plejer</"
"guilabel>. Samo odznaite <guilabel> Prikaži poruku u iskačućem prozoru</"
"guilabel> stavku za <guimenuitem>JuK  pokrenut u dok modu</guimenuitem>. "
"Više informacija o &kde; postavkama notifikacija možete nači <ulink url="
"\"help:/kcontrol/kcmnotify\">ovdje</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Popup Track Announcement</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Iskačući prozor najave pjesme</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle option. If enabled, &juk; will display an indicator "
"whenever a song starts playing, with information on the artist and title, "
"and with buttons allowing you to quickly switch to a different song. The "
"Dock in System Tray option must also be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je uključi/isključi ocpija. Ako je uključena, &juk; će prikazati "
"indikator kad god pjesma počinje pjevati, sa informacijama o izvođaču i "
"nazivu , i sa dugmadima kako koji vam omogućuju da brzo preskočite na "
"sljedeću pjesmu. Opcija Dok u Sistemskom izborniku mora takođe biti "
"uključena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1526
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tag Guesser...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pogađač tagova...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration"
"\">Tag Guesser Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the "
"patterns used to guess tag information from filenames."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda otvara <link linkend=\"juk-tag-guesser-configuration\"> "
"Konfiguracijski dijalog pogađača tagova </link> gdje možete promijeniti "
"obrazac korišten za pogađanje informacija iz imena datoteka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1538
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>File Renamer...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preimenilac datoteka...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command brings up the <link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">File Renamer "
"Configuration dialog box</link>, where you can alter the way &juk; renames "
"files for you."
msgstr ""
"Ova komanda otvara  <link linkend=\"juk-rename-dialog\">Dijalog "
"Konfiguracija preimenovanje datoteka</link>, gdje možete mijenjati način na "
"koji &juk; preimenuje datoteke za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1552
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally &juk; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
#| "<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
#| "sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-settings"
#| "\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
#| "html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgid ""
"Additionally &juk; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Dodatno &juk; ima zajedničke sa &kde; <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu> i "
"<guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu> stavke menija, za više informacija pročitajte "
"odjeljke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-settings\">Postavke "
"Meni</ulink> i <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-help\">Meni "
"Pomoć</ulink> &kde; osnova."

